msgid ""
"During boot the console will display messages that have ascii control "
"characters.  This make it hard to read. Especialy during a disk check.  To "
"correct this make sure bashrc has something similar to the following: # "
"Provides a colored /bin/ls command.  Used in conjunction with code in # "
"/etc/profile."
